<text id="02-output-contract" title="handoff-id-payload Output Contract" version="1.0.0" est_tokens="900" depth="essential">
  <summary>JSON Schema for the handoff payload and SupervisorDecision.</summary>

  <section title="Handoff payload schema">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$id": "handoff-id-payload/handoff",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ["task_id", "target_agent", "decision_metadata"],
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "properties": {
    "task_id":      {"type": "string", "pattern": "^[a-zA-Z0-9_-]{1,64}$"},
    "target_agent": {"type": "string", "minLength": 1},
    "decision_metadata": {"type": "object"}
  }
}
    ]]></code>
  </section>

  <section title="SupervisorDecision schema">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$id": "handoff-id-payload/supervisor-decision",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ["target_agent", "reason"],
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "properties": {
    "target_agent":     {"type": "string"},
    "reason":           {"type": "string", "minLength": 4, "maxLength": 300},
    "decision_metadata": {"type": "object"}
  }
}
    ]]></code>
  </section>

  <section title="Good example (handoff)">
    <example type="good">
      <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "task_id": "t_8821",
  "target_agent": "neromedia_writer",
  "decision_metadata": {"category": "AI", "lang": "uk", "source_count": 3}
}
      ]]></code>
      <note>53 bytes; the writer pulls the 3 source articles from `/srv/nero/queue/t_8821.json` on receipt.</note>
    </example>
  </section>

  <section title="Bad example (conversation forwarding)">
    <example type="bad">
      <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "to": "neromedia_writer",
  "history": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "<6KB original article + classifier's full chain-of-thought>"}
  ]
}
      ]]></code>
      <note>No task_id; classifier reasoning leaks into every downstream agent. Validator rejects.</note>
    </example>
  </section>

  <section title="Self-check checklist">
    <list>
      <item>Payload has `task_id`, `target_agent`, `decision_metadata` only.</item>
      <item>No conversation history, no raw input, no prior agent's reasoning.</item>
      <item>Supervisor emissions are structured SupervisorDecision objects.</item>
    </list>
  </section>
</text>
